    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Populate mindspree_prod row\n\nClick **Execute workflow** to upsert the `mindspree_prod` row in `cs_project_config`.\nMatches on `project_key` — safe to re-run (idempotent).\n\nValues resolved by name-matching LoveStyle prod Zendesk objects to Mindspree\n(macros / ticket_fields / custom_statuses). 30 real values set.\n\n## ⚠️ FILL BEFORE RUNNING (left blank — env/secret values only you have)\n- `payments_api_base_url`\n- `slack_automation_errors_channel_id`\n- `slack_dev_error_channel_id`\n- `classification_model_id`  (note: FT model output must be remapped to Mindspree slugs — see below)\n- `classification_confidence_threshold`\n- `message_limit_threshold`\n- `hmac_key_id`  (suggested: mindspree-prod)\n- `refund_macro_upsell_id`  (available in Mindspree: 37108985099805 \"Refund upsell - Automation\")\n- `refund_macro_rejection_alt_id`  (available: 35098642651933 \"Refund Rejection:: Final Answer\")\n\n## Left at 0 = feature disabled / object missing in Mindspree\nObjects that DO NOT EXIST in Mindspree yet — create them before enabling that branch:\n- `ticket_custom_status_chatbot_automated_id` — no \"Automated\" custom status\n- `ticket_custom_field_automation_label_id` — no \"Automation classification\" field\n- `ticket_field_contact_form_classification_id` — no \"Contact form classification\" field\n- `ticket_field_chatbot_classification_id` — no \"Chatbot classification\" field\nAgreed-empty (semantic match declined / no equivalent):\n- `macro_single_refund_complaint`, `macro_account_deletion_id`, `refund_macro_rejection_id`,\n  `macro_cancellation_confirmation`, `macro_refund_confirmation`\nEmpty in lovestyle_prod reference too:\n- `ticket_field_allow_automation`, `refund_macro_no_upsell_to_refund_id`\nUNRESOLVED — needs decode:\n- `macro_cancellation_failed_payment_id` — lovestyle_prod uses 24546952679964, but that macro's\n  TITLE wasn't in the decoded LoveStyle set, so no Mindspree name-match was possible.\n  Supply the LS macro title (or re-scan Mindspree automation-macro page) to fill this.\n\n## Value quirks vs LoveStyle (verified against Mindspree API, do NOT \"correct\")\n- refund_value_* use TRIPLE underscore (\"refund___...\") — Mindspree named options \"Refund:: \" (with space).\n- `refund_value_upsell` = \"refund___upsells\" (PLURAL in Mindspree).\n- `ticket_field_language_id` -> \"Language Email\" (34842181901341). Its options are full words\n  (\"english\",\"spanish\",\"deutsch\"...), NOT 2-letter codes. Language-write logic + FT classifier\n  output must be remapped to these slugs or the write will fail.\n\n## After running\nVerify the row in the data table view, then archive this workflow.",
        "height": 720,
        "width": 720,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "e06ed06e-7f64-4c57-b319-1ce586ba3e87",
      "name": "How to use",
